257
00:24:13,318 --> 00:24:15,843
with ulcers as bad
as any middle-aged businessman.

258
00:24:15,954 --> 00:24:17,979
Okay, I get the picture.

259
00:24:19,458 --> 00:24:22,188
- Now can I take her home?
