319
00:29:14,018 --> 00:29:15,781
Oh, God, I love you.

320
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:22,154
But you didn't protect me.

321
00:29:22,894 --> 00:29:24,361
And you should have.

322
00:29:24,929 --> 00:29:27,227
