435
00:38:32,576 --> 00:38:35,773
Are you saying that
I'm just supposed to bury the girl's mother...

436
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,575
and not tell her about it?

437
00:38:37,815 --> 00:38:39,749
Yes, that's what I'm saying.

438
00:38:41,552 --> 00:38:46,080
You are one ignorant son of a bitch,
Dr. Raglan.

439
00:38:51,295 --> 00:38:53,422
Now, I have left my phone number...

440
00:38:54,332 --> 00:38:55,924
on your front desk.

441
00:38:57,068 --> 00:39:00,299
