443
00:39:10,114 --> 00:39:11,809
Shall I have him stopped?

444
00:39:12,516 --> 00:39:13,949
No, it's all right.

445
00:39:14,685 --> 00:39:15,777
He's drunk.

446
00:39:58,262 --> 00:40:00,230
Hi. Sorry I'm late.

447
00:40:01,699 --> 00:40:04,361
- You two look like you're having fun.
