450
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:11,675
Candy...

451
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:14,171
We could if she wanted to.

452
00:40:16,380 --> 00:40:17,745
What do you think?

453
00:40:18,349 --> 00:40:19,475
Well, I...

