455
00:40:24,955 --> 00:40:25,922
Sure.

456
00:40:32,563 --> 00:40:35,123
As soon as Candy realized
she had me alone...

457
00:40:35,232 --> 00:40:37,928
she got me to play
"mother and daughter" with her.

458
00:40:40,204 --> 00:40:43,002
