against her parents, under therapy...

762
01:15:54,683 --> 01:15:56,310
then they killed them.

763
01:15:57,219 --> 01:15:59,653
I know, I didn't want to believe that...

764
01:16:00,255 --> 01:16:02,086
but now they've killed Ruth Mayer...

765
01:16:02,257 --> 01:16:05,886
and they could kill you or me,
and she wouldn't even be aware of it.

766
01:16:06,995 --> 01:16:09,725
I mean, she doesn't even know
that Candy's here.

767
01:16:13,068 --> 01:16:15,764
- I want Candice back.
- Then do it my way.

768
01:16:17,039 --> 01:16:18,006
Please.

769
01:16:18,974 --> 01:16:20,407
It's the right way.

770
01:16:22,911 --> 01:16:24,606
What do you want me to do?

771
01:16:25,514 --> 01:16:27,778
I want you to go back into that hut...

772
01:16:28,083 --> 01:16:30,574
and persuade Nola that you want her back...

773
01:16:31,620 --> 01:16:33,588
that you want your family back.

774
01:16:33,855 --> 01:16:37,347
I want you to play the role
of apologetic lover and husband.

775
01:16:37,960 --> 01:16:38,949
Why?

776
01:16:39,261 --> 01:16:41,855
Because if you can keep Nola
calm and happy...

777
01:16:42,264 --> 01:16:44,095
then the brood's neutral.

778
01:16:44,766 --> 01:16:48,258
If she's mellow,
then I can just walk into that attic...

779
01:16:49,338 --> 01:16:52,136
pick up Candy,
tuck her under my arm and walk out.

780
01:16:53,108 --> 01:16:54,598
Now, can you do that?

781
01:16:58,013 --> 01:16:59,275
I don't know.

782
01:17:00,315 --> 01:17:02,180
Frank, if things go wrong...

783
01:17:03,285 --> 01:17:05,947
if Nola gets angry, if the kids get angry...

784
01:17:08,490 --> 01:17:09,957
You understand?

785
01:17:10,926 --> 01:17:13,952
I'm not going to be the only one
to pay for that anger.

786
01:17:14,296 --> 01:17:16,025
Raglan, I don't trust you.

787
01:17:19,368 --> 01:17:21,165
What does it matter?

788
01:17:22,604 --> 01:17:25,266
I'll move up there 30 seconds after you're in.

789
01:17:34,883 --> 01:17:36,748
Frank, be nice to her.

790
01:18:13,221 --> 01:18:14,279
Hal?

791
01:18:16,792 --> 01:18:19,386
It's me, Nola. It's Frank.

792
01:18:25,467 --> 01:18:26,695
Am I dreaming?

793
01:18:27,969 --> 01:18:31,905
I thought you said you weren't going to
come and see me while I was here.

794
01:18:34,943 --> 01:18:37,104
I think that was a misunderstanding.

795
01:18:42,551 --> 01:18:44,041
That's why I'm here.

796
01:18:46,054 --> 01:18:48,181
I want us to understand each other.

797
01:19:30,632 --> 01:19:33,100
You're the only woman in the world for me.

798
01:19:33,435 --> 01:19:35,926
You always have been, you always will be.

799
01:19:37,939 --> 01:19:39,566
It won't ever change.

800
01:19:41,009 --> 01:19:42,670
I want you to know that.

801
01:19:43,178 --> 01:19:46,238
I wish it were true. God, I wish it were true.

802
01:20:16,478 --> 01:20:17,706
We lost touch.

803
01:20:19,514 --> 01:20:22,108
That's the only reason
all this ever happened.

804
01:20:23,118 --> 01:20:26,576
All we have to do
is make sure we don't lose touch again.

805
01:20:28,723 --> 01:20:31,214
Isolation is part of my therapy.

806
01:20:33,295 --> 01:20:36,628
What's been happening to me
has been just too strange...

807
01:20:37,365 --> 01:20:41,165
too strange for me to share
with anyone from my old life.

808
01:20:43,505 --> 01:20:45,735
Then make me a part of your new life.

809
01:20:46,908 --> 01:20:48,466
Let me be part of it.

810
01:20:50,178 --> 01:20:52,578
Show me, educate me, involve me.

811
01:20:53,415 --> 01:20:56,213
I'm ready now.
I wasn't before, but I'm ready now.

812
01:21:07,429 --> 01:21:08,589
Candy?

813
01:21:14,502 --> 01:21:16,299
Are you ready for me, Frank?

814
01:21:18,340 --> 01:21:19,705
Are you really?

815
01:21:22,177 --> 01:21:24,407
I seem to be a very special person.

816
01:21:25,146 --> 01:21:27,910
I'm in the middle of a strange adventure.

817
01:21:30,485 --> 01:21:31,918
Let me be with you.

818
01:21:34,189 --> 01:21:36,453
I want to go with you wherever you go.

819
01:21:37,425 --> 01:21:38,392
Do you?

820
01:21:42,497 --> 01:21:43,464
Do you?

821
01:21:46,067 --> 01:21:47,034
Yes.

822
01:21:48,637 --> 01:21:49,934
Then look.

823
01:22:32,414 --> 01:22:33,381
Daddy?

824
01:22:34,783 --> 01:22:37,149
Is it time to go to school yet?

825
01:22:38,153 --> 01:22:39,450
No, sweetheart.

826
01:22:40,722 --> 01:22:41,984
It's Dr. Hal.

827
01:22:43,024 --> 01:22:45,458
And Daddy's downstairs talking to Mommy.

828
01:22:46,328 --> 01:22:47,795
He wants to see you.

829
01:24:02,170 --> 01:24:03,535
Oh, God, Nola.

830
01:24:05,840 --> 01:24:08,673
No, I disgust you.

831
01:24:12,147 --> 01:24:13,637
I sicken you.

832
01:24:14,049 --> 01:24:15,880
You hate me.

833
01:24:18,319 --> 01:24:20,879
You didn't come here because you love me.

834
01:24:21,322 --> 01:24:25,088
You came here to take our daughter away
and give her to somebody else.

835
01:24:29,397 --> 01:24:30,989
I wouldn't do that.

836
01:24:31,933 --> 01:24:33,457
I wouldn't do that to you.

837
01:24:41,776 --> 01:24:44,870
You go out of that door.
You find your daddy.

838
01:24:51,086 --> 01:24:53,577
You liar. You're lying.

839
01:24:55,323 --> 01:24:58,622
You're lying! I know!

840
01:25:42,403 --> 01:25:46,032
I know you so well, and it won't work.

841
01:25:48,576 --> 01:25:51,943
I'd kill Candice
before I let you take her away from me.

842
01:25:52,614 --> 01:25:54,104
Do you hear me?

843
01:25:55,150 --> 01:25:58,449
I'd kill Candice before I let you take her!

844
01:26:36,357 --> 01:26:37,619
Make them stop.

845
01:26:46,201 --> 01:26:48,601
They're doing what you want them to do.

846
01:26:54,642 --> 01:26:56,234
You want them to kill Candice.

847
01:27:00,648 --> 01:27:03,208
You make them stop, or I'll kill you.

848
01:27:03,451 --> 01:27:05,009
Kill me.

849
01:29:35,603 --> 01:29:37,161
We're going home, Candy.

850
01:29:40,274 --> 01:29:41,400
We're going home.

